sorry to say- but maybe better here in a not so sensitive env than elsewhere:
it is called _tera_, not terra - terra is latin for earth, tera is greek prefix for 10 to the power of twelve - as in kilo, mega, giga, .. tera
if you do this with the wrong audience, you can just as well save your breath and go home
